企洗定個八月十五。on9仔有時好kai，如果佢因為錦而以後唔再on9，你地仲邊有得笑? 我勸你地推之前先三思，唔好比班花生友影響，呢d人有野串就唔會理其他人感受，當中仲有成萬個準會考生捧蛋嫁，希望你地可以作出獨立判斷，唔好推爆個post，做埋哂d捐人不利已既事。<br />\n<br />\nP.S 樓主一定係硬膠，想知佢點膠睇呢個POST就知，諗都唔洗諗。</blockquote><br />\n吹大ｄ啦<br />\n精神病人"},{"pid":"3f42238cb19d38d47708a118133f346a8f086b1e","tid":389811,"uid":52560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"搭地鐵上連/高登不嬲都係極危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdbf6d3af2e931e924a6961e00a3854f11ea1ce","tid":389811,"uid":128223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aaf41e8fd2daa851e4339cc83d5998e27304ada5","tid":389811,"uid":128921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"真係on9得可以，香港咁大竟然亂鳩估樓主住黃大仙"},{"pid":"88a5fa22be4d3c06509d0143609e1ee547ab216a","tid":389811,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/000157_9c1a020050cceec581f9742b9ed6e176.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F000157_9c1a020050cceec581f9742b9ed6e176.jpg&h=da115252&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}